  running from the date direct involvement ceased. Separately, staff
  at salary band I or above involved in supervisory activities must
  notify the Compliance and Governance Office before accepting any
  occupational activity for a period of two years from the date their
  involvement in supervisory activities ceased. (ECB Staff Rules,
